---
title: Erie Day of Code 2016 | June 17 @ <%= venue.name %>
---

<div class="home">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-12">
      <%= image_tag 'venue.jpg', alt: venue.name, title: venue.name, class: 'venue-photo' %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="mailing-list-signup">
    <h1>Stay up to Date</h1>
    <h2>Subscribe to our mailing list for updates and ticket sales</h2>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-12">
        <form action="<%= mailing_list_url %>"
              id="mailing-list-subscribe-form"
              class="form"
              method="post"
              name="mc-embedded-subscribe-form"
              target="_blank">
          <div class="form-group row">
            <label class="sr-only" for="email">Email Address</label>
            <div class="col-lg-10">
              <input type="email"
                     class="form-control form-control-lg"
                     id="email"
                     name="EMAIL"
                     placeholder="Enter Email Address">
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-2">
              <input class="btn btn-primary btn-block btn-lg"
                     name="subscribe"
                     type="submit"
                     value="Subscribe" />
            </div>
          </div>

          <div style="position: absolute; left: -5000px;">
            <input name="b_3fcd98d64025f034a082fe384_bb907d9e18"
                   tabindex="-1"
                   type="text" />
          </div>
        </form>
        </div>
      </div>
  </section>

  <section id="speakers">
    <h1>Speakers</h1>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-6">
        <article class="speaker">
          <%= image_tag 'speakers/adam-wathan.jpg', class: 'speaker-photo', alt: 'Adam Wathan' %>
          <h3 class="name">
            <%= link_to "Adam Wathan", "https://twitter.com/adamwathan" %>
          </h3>
          <p class="info">
            Host of <%= link_to "Full Stack Radio", "https://twitter.com/fullstackradio" %>.
            Senior Developer at <%= link_to "Tighten Co.", "http://tighten.co" %>.
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>

      <div class="col-lg-6">
        <article class="speaker">
          <%= image_tag 'speakers/jesse-and-caryn.jpg', class: 'speaker-photo', alt: "Jesse O'Brien & Caryn Humphreys" %>
          <h3 class="name">
            <%= link_to "Jesse O'Brien", "https://twitter.com/jesseobrien_" %>
            &
            <%= link_to "Caryn Humphreys", "https://twitter.com/ladycarni" %>
          </h3>
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
              <p class="info">
                Laravel old guard, Golang and Space enthusiast.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
              <p class="info">
                UX aficionado, board gamer, expat currently conquering Canada
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="info">
            Web Developer and Product Designer at
            <%= link_to "Vehikl", "http://vehikl.com" %>.
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="more-speakers-coming site-notice">More to be announced soon!</p>
  </section>

  <section id="venue">
    <h1>Venue</h1>
    <!--
    <p>COMPLETELY AWESOME IMAGE OF BUILDING</p>
    <h2 class="name"><%= link_to venue.name, venue.url %></h2>
    <address>
      <p><%= venue.street %></p>
      <p><%= venue.address_line %></p>
    </address>
    -->

    <p>
      The Erie Art Museum is one of the best places in Erie to hold events.
      The historic downtown gallery building blows out to include an enormous
      modern architectural wing with an event space and café. The building spans
      most of the block between 4th and State St., and 5th and French St.
      The conference entrance will be through the large glass doors of the
      Wave Café on 5th street. Once inside, the large gallery hall with the main
      stage for Erie Day of Code will be immediately to your left.
      You're more than welcome to check out the various collections at the museum
      during intermissions or lunch the conference for free!
    </p>

    <div class="embedded-map hidden-sm-down">
      <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m14!1m8!1m3!1d11835.628400315789!2d-80.085217!3d42.130872!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x0%3A0x24059a439df897ed!2sErie+Art+Museum!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sus!4v1458431315024" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0" allowfullscreen></iframe>
    </div>

    <article id="parking">
      <p class="site-notice">Parking information coming soon</p>
    </article>
  </section>

  <section id="lodging">
    <h1>Lodging</h1>
    <p>
      Tourism is huge in Erie, so if you're coming in from out of town there are
      plenty of places for you to stay. Here are some options near by:
    </p>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-6">
        <h2>Walking Distance</h2>
        <% close_lodging.each do |place| %>
          <article class="place">
            <h3><%= link_to place.name, place.url %></h3>
            <div class="contact">
              <address>
                <p class="distance"><%= place.distance %> from the Venue</p>
                <p>
                  <%= place.address %>
                  (<%= link_to "Directions", place.directions, target: '_blank' %>)
                </p>
                <p><%= "#{place.city_state}, #{place.zipcode}" %></p>
                <p>
                  <a href="tel:+1<%= place.phone.gsub(/[^\d]/, "") %>">
                    <%= place.phone %>
                  </a>
                </p>
              </address>
              <p><%= place.reason %></p>
            </div>
          </article>
        <% end %>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-6">
        <h2>A Bit Further With Attractions</h2>
        <% further_lodging.each do |place| %>
          <article class="place">
            <h3><%= link_to place.name, place.url %></h3>
            <div class="contact">
              <address>
                <p class="distance"><%= place.distance %> from the Venue</p>
                <p>
                  <%= place.address %>
                  (<%= link_to "Directions", place.directions, target: '_blank' %>)
                </p>
                <p><%= "#{place.city_state}, #{place.zipcode}" %></p>
                <p>
                  <a href="tel:+1<%= place.phone.gsub(/[^\d]/, "") %>">
                    <%= place.phone %>
                  </a>
                </p>
              </address>
              <p><%= place.reason %></p>
            </div>

          </article>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-6 col-lg-offset-3">
        <p class="site-notice">
          If you'd prefer to avoid walking or driving to and from the venue while in
          town, Erie has a <%= link_to "bus line", data.info.bus_line_url %>
          that runs up on State St. most of the day and Uber has service here as
          well.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="sponsors">
    <h1>Sponsors</h1>
    <h4 class="prospectus-text site-notice">
      Interested in sponsoring?  Check out our
      <%= link_to 'Prospectus', "/edoc2016-prospectus.pdf", class: 'prospectus-link', target: '_blank' %>
      for information.
    </h4>

    <section id="sponsor-partners">
      <h1 class="partners">Partners</h1>

      <div class="row">
        <% data.sponsors.partners.each do |s| %>
          <div class="col-lg-6">
            <article class="sponsor">
              <% link_to s.url do %>
                <%= image_tag "sponsors/#{s.logo}", alt: s.name, title: s.name, class: 'logo' %>
              <% end %>
            </article>
          </div>
        <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </section>
</div>
